---
// src/pages/services/built-in-refrigerator-repair.astro
// Audit pass 2026-04-23 (C14 PRIMARY HYBRID audit-primary v1.3 novel 2nd application):
// Schema Pattern A migration (body <script> → Fragment slot="head-scripts"), phone (323) → (424) primary,
// tier H2 structure (3 tiers × 27 brands), brand-index block, cross-links DOWN to 7 new luxury combos,
// cross-links UP to /services/refrigerator-repair/ + /services/freezer-repair/ (matched-column suite).

import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ServiceHero from '../../components/ServiceHero.astro';
import { MAIN_PHONE } from '../../data/branches';

const title = "Built-In Refrigerator Repair, Sub-Zero + Column Luxury Across SoCal";
const description = "$89 diagnostic waived with repair. Sub-Zero, Liebherr, Thermador, Miele, Viking, GE Monogram, True column built-in across LA, Orange, Ventura, San Bernardino & Riverside counties. BHGS Licensed #A49573. EPA 608 Universal certified #1346255700410.";
const canonical = "https://samedayappliance.repair/services/built-in-refrigerator-repair/";
const phone = MAIN_PHONE.display;
const phoneRaw = MAIN_PHONE.raw;
const phoneHref = MAIN_PHONE.href;

const faqs = [
  { q: "How much does built-in refrigerator repair cost?", a: "Our diagnostic fee is $89, waived when you approve the repair. Built-in refrigerator repairs typically run $200–$700 depending on the component and brand. Thermostat, fan motor, or evaporator defrost repair is toward the lower end. Compressor replacement on a Sub-Zero, Thermador, or Miele built-in is $600–$1,200+. Given that quality built-in refrigerators cost $6,000–$20,000+, repair is almost always the right decision at these price points." },
  { q: "Which areas of Southern California do you cover for built-in refrigerator repair?", a: "Same-day across Los Angeles, Orange, Ventura, San Bernardino, and Riverside counties, Bel Air, Beverly Hills, Brentwood, Pacific Palisades, and Malibu in LA's luxury core; Newport Coast, Pelican Hill, and Newport Beach in OC; Westlake Village, Hidden Hills, and Calabasas-adjacent in Ventura; Rancho Cucamonga, Riverside, and Temecula wine country estates in the Inland Empire. Eight service territories total. Sub-Zero, Liebherr, Thermador, Miele, Viking, GE Monogram, True Residential, every luxury column built-in brand running SoCal kitchens. BHGS Licensed #A49573." },
  { q: "What makes repairing a built-in refrigerator different from a freestanding model?", a: "Three key differences: (1) Access, built-in refrigerators ventilate through the front grille, not the rear. They're installed flush with cabinetry and cannot be pulled out for rear access. All service must be done from the front or through the interior. (2) Components, built-in models use commercial-grade compressors, more sophisticated control systems, and in Sub-Zero's case, dual separate compressor systems. (3) Panel-ready models, refrigerators with custom cabinetry panels require careful handling to avoid damaging the cabinetry during service." },
  { q: "My Sub-Zero refrigerator is not cooling, what should I check first?", a: "Check the vacuum condenser first. Sub-Zero built-ins have a vacuum condenser that requires cleaning every 12 months, when it's clogged with dust and debris, the compressor overheats and the refrigerator loses cooling capacity. The condenser is accessed through the front grille at the bottom. If cleaning the condenser doesn't restore cooling within 24 hours, call us, it may be a compressor, sealed system, or control board issue that requires diagnosis." },
  { q: "Is it worth repairing a Sub-Zero or Miele built-in refrigerator vs replacing it?", a: "Almost always yes for quality built-in refrigerators. Sub-Zero, Liebherr, Thermador, Miele, Viking, and GE Monogram built-ins are designed and built to last 20+ years with proper service. A $500 compressor repair on a $15,000 Sub-Zero is 3% of replacement cost. Even a $1,200 sealed system repair on an 18-year-old unit is almost always better than $15,000+ for a replacement. We'll give you the repair cost upfront so you can make the decision with full information, but for quality built-ins, repair is almost universally the right call." },
  { q: "Do you repair Sub-Zero, Thermador, Miele, Liebherr, Viking, GE Monogram, and True Residential built-in refrigerators?", a: "Yes, those seven are the luxury column built-in brands we service with dedicated combo pages: Sub-Zero built-in · Liebherr · Thermador · Miele (+ Miele Pro disambig) · Viking · GE Monogram · True Residential. We also repair Gaggenau, Dacor, Jenn-Air, Fisher & Paykel, SKS, BlueStar, Hestan, Bertazzoni luxury tier + KitchenAid, Bosch, Electrolux (+Pro disambig), GE Profile, GE Cafe, Fulgor Milano, ILVE, Smeg premium tier + Perlick, U-Line, Marvel, Big Chill undercounter tier. Parts sourced through brand-specific luxury appliance distributors." },
  { q: "What is Sub-Zero's dual compressor system and why does it matter for repair?", a: "Sub-Zero built-in refrigerators use two separate compressors, one dedicated to the refrigerator section and one to the freezer section. This is different from every other refrigerator brand which uses a single compressor for both. The benefit is independent temperature control and longer food preservation. For repair, it means diagnosing which compressor system has failed. If only the refrigerator section is warm while the freezer is fine (or vice versa), that pinpoints which compressor circuit to service." },
  { q: "What are the main built-in refrigerator form factors?", a: "Four common LA luxury built-in configurations: (1) Column, 18\" / 24\" / 30\" / 36\" / 48\" single-function columns (refrigerator-only or freezer-only) that combine for matched-pair column suites (e.g., 36\" refrigerator column + 36\" freezer column + optional wine cooler column); signature of Sub-Zero / Liebherr / Thermador Freedom / Miele MasterCool / Viking Virtuoso / GE Monogram Statement / True. (2) Standard built-in, traditional 36\" / 42\" / 48\" side-by-side or French-door built-in that installs flush with cabinets; Sub-Zero Classic + Thermador Pro + Jenn-Air + KitchenAid. (3) Integrated panel-ready, refrigerator accepts a full-overlay custom cabinetry panel, visually indistinguishable from surrounding cabinets when installed; Sub-Zero Integrated + Miele MasterCool Integrated + Thermador Freedom. (4) Refrigerator drawers, 24\" or 30\" drawer-format integrated units often installed at islands or secondary-zone locations; Sub-Zero ID-30C + Thermador + KitchenAid. Service approach adapts to form factor, integrated units require panel-protection discipline, columns require matched-pair coordination." }
];

const schemaJsons = [
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "Service", "serviceType": "Built-In Refrigerator Repair",
    "name": "Built-In Refrigerator Repair",
    "description": "Luxury built-in refrigerator repair across Southern California, Sub-Zero, Liebherr, Thermador, Miele, Viking, GE Monogram, True Residential column specialists + panel-ready integrated + refrigerator drawers. Front-ventilated commercial-grade compressor service, brand-specific OEM parts. BHGS Licensed #A49573. $89 residential diagnostic waived with repair.",
    "provider": {
      "@type": "LocalBusiness",
      "name": "Same Day Appliance Repair",
      "telephone": phone,
      "url": "https://samedayappliance.repair/",
      "priceRange": "$$$$"
    },
    "areaServed": [
      {"@type":"AdministrativeArea","name":"Los Angeles County"},
      {"@type":"AdministrativeArea","name":"Orange County"},
      {"@type":"AdministrativeArea","name":"Ventura County"},
      {"@type":"AdministrativeArea","name":"San Bernardino County"},
      {"@type":"AdministrativeArea","name":"Riverside County"}
    ],
    "offers": { "@type": "Offer", "priceSpecification": { "@type": "PriceSpecification", "price": "89.00", "priceCurrency": "USD", "description": "Residential diagnostic fee, waived with repair" } }
  },
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "FAQPage", "mainEntity": faqs.map(f => ({ "@type": "Question", "name": f.q, "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": f.a } })) },
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Services", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/services/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Built-In Refrigerator Repair", "item": canonical }
    ]
  }
];
---

