          <li>BHGS Licensed #A49573</li>
          <li>Sub-Zero dual compressor specialists</li>
          <li>Column · panel-ready · integrated</li>
          <li>Liebherr · Thermador · Miele · Viking</li>
          <li>GE Monogram · True Residential</li>
          <li>5-county SoCal coverage</li>
        </ul>
      </aside>
