    <div class="form-factor-grid">
      <div class="ff-card">
        <h4>Column (18" / 24" / 30" / 36" / 48")</h4>
        <p>Single-function columns (refrigerator-only or freezer-only). Pair into matched suites, e.g., 36" refrigerator column + 36" freezer column + optional wine cooler column. Signature of Sub-Zero + Liebherr + Thermador Freedom + Miele MasterCool + Viking Virtuoso + GE Monogram Statement + True Residential. Column-to-column cold-bridge + synchronized control matter for suite service.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ff-card">
        <h4>Standard built-in</h4>
        <p>Traditional 36" / 42" / 48" side-by-side or French-door built-in flush with cabinets. Sub-Zero Classic + Thermador Pro + Jenn-Air + KitchenAid + Bosch. Front-ventilated; full-height single-unit dual-zone with single or dual compressor architecture.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ff-card">
        <h4>Integrated panel-ready</h4>
        <p>Accepts a full-overlay custom cabinetry panel; visually indistinguishable from surrounding cabinets when installed. Sub-Zero Integrated + Miele MasterCool Integrated + Thermador Freedom + Liebherr Monolith. Requires panel-protection discipline during any exterior-adjacent service to preserve finish.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ff-card">
        <h4>Refrigerator drawers (24" / 30")</h4>
        <p>Drawer-format integrated units often installed at kitchen islands or secondary-zone locations (pantry, home office wet bar, butler's pantry). Sub-Zero ID-30C + Thermador + KitchenAid + U-Line + Perlick. Drawer-mechanism service + temperature-zone control common service items.</p>
